Here is an example of how to generate a table of contents automatically in a LaTeX document:
```
\documentclass{article}

% Make sure to include the tocdepth package to control the depth of the TOC
\usepackage{tocdepth}

% Set the depth of the TOC to  , which means sections and subsections will be included
